oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Bovine Practitioners, American Association of
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Following the grand opening ceremony, the stage was set for lots of fun, good food and entertainment in the blazing sun of the Sunshine State. The spouse hospitality reception on Thursday evening organized by Gatz and Kay Riddell and their local arrangements committee was well attended for a presentation by Bob Morris entitled "Welcome to Florida - How Soon Will You Be Leaving?"
